author:
Neill Ostrout
Journal Inquirer
title: Huskies enjoy 'homecoming'
text:
Journal Inquirer Journal Inquirer | 0 comments 
ORLANDO, Fla. — Eleven members of the UConn football team grew up in the state of Florida. 
They may not have been the happiest 11 Huskies after their team’s 40-13 demolition of Central Florida Saturday night but they were likely close. 
Among the key contributors to the Huskies’ win was cornerback Jhavon Williams.
